<L>Shall for a moment, from him&s;elf &s;et free,</L>
<L>Lean on his Crutch, and pipe forth prai&s;e to M$.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>Rejoice, ye happy GOTHAMITES, rejoice;</L>
