<L>The <HI>Je&s;&s;amine,</HI> with which the Queen of flow'rs</L>
<L>To charm her God adorns his fav'rite bow'rs,</L>
<L>Which Brides, by the plain hand of n$atne&s;s dre&s;t,</L>
