<L>It&s;elf a Grove, gave our fir&s;t Parents cloaths;</L>
<L>The <HI>Vine,</HI> which, like a blu&s;hing new-made Bride,</L>
<L>Clu&s;t'ring, empurples all the Mountain's &s;ide;</L>
<L><PB N="111" REF="107">
The <HI>Yew,</HI> which, in the place of &s;culptur'd &s;tone,</L>
